<div class="info-card tile-about accent-teal">
  <div class="card-content">
    <h3>About Us</h3>
    <p>We are the <strong>official Capture the Flag hacking team</strong> of the <strong>University of Genoa</strong>. Composed of Bachelor's and Master's students united by a passion for cybersecurity, we actively improve our skills in national and international competitions.</p>

    <p>Our name comes from <strong>pwn</strong> + <strong>panissa</strong>, a traditional Ligurian street food made from fried chickpeas.</p>
  </div>
</div>

